headline: Effectual Appoints Ashish Dhawan, SVP and CRO of NetApp's Cloud Business Unit, to Board of Directors
summary: Effectual, an AWS Premier Tier Services Partner, today announced the appointment of Ashish Dhawan, Senior Vice President and Chief Revenue Officer of NetApp's Cloud Business Unit, to its Board of Directors. This strategic addition further solidifies Effectual's leadership in enterprise cloud modernization and underscores its unwavering commitment to driving seamless cloud-native migrations to AWS.
